{
  "stem": "280.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By no means, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our closest neighbor were non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a daughter my age, and we were actually very close friends, and we were in each other's homes frequently.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my parents had neighbors, non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were their-- they were very good neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, we were not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Los Angeles had three type of Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I am sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were the Orthodox [? image ?] we were part of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot tell you which segment was the larger one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there were Status Quo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess you would compare it to Reform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then there were Neolog.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, pardon me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Status Quo would be like Conservative, and the Neolog would be like Reform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the Status Quo had also a beautiful synagogue, which was-- what shall I tell you-- the-- the real [INAUDIBLE] Jews call a synagogue kosher, the one which is segregated properly.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the one which is not segregated properly is not such a kosher synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So this was also-- because the women were upstairs, but you could see downstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a beautiful building, again, and the-- the chief rabbi was a doctor rabbiner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had a doctorate in philosophy, a very imposing, elegant man, very intelligent and highly educated and secularly also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Klein. ?] And then was the Reform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- we had very little contact with that-- the other segments of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had some because I went to [ROMANIAN] with some of the-- Status Quo, and I was in some of their homes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were lovely people, but not observant like we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was-- they lived a very nice social life.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
